ISLAMABAD, Jul 07 (APP): Director General, First Political Division, Ministry of Foreign Affairs Afghanistan, Mufti Noor Ahmad Noor, called on the Foreign Secretary (FS), Amna Baloch on Monday at the successful conclusion of the First Round of Pakistan-Afghan Political Consultations.
The Foreign Secretary stressed on regular engagement to deepen ties, address concerns and promote regional peace and prosperity.
